<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  .body { font-family: 'Helvetica', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #fef2f2; padding: 20px; }
  .card { max-width: 500px; background: #ffffff; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
  .header { background-color: #ef4444; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
  .content { padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.6; }
  .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; padding: 20px; }
  .btn { background: #dc2626; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; }
  /* Box for important data preservation info */
  .info-box { background: #fff1f2; border: 1px dashed #f43f5e; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; color: #991b1b; font-size: 14px; text-align: left; }
</style>
</head>
<body class="body">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="100" alt="{{company}} Logo">
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2 style="color: #991b1b;">Account Deactivated</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Your account at <strong>{{company}}</strong> has been successfully deactivated.</p>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Important:</strong> Your profile is hidden and notifications are disabled, but your <strong>data is preserved in our database</strong>. You won't lose any of your history or settings.
      </div>
      
      <p>You can return at any time by logging back in below.</p>
      <br>
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="btn">Reactivate My Account</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© {{year}} {{company}} | Privacy Policy</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
